title: AJ Styles
summary: Allen Neal Jones (born June 2, 1977), better known by his ring name AJ Styles (also stylized as A.J. Styles), is an American professional wrestler currently signed to WWE, where he performs on the Raw brand. He is universally recognized as one of the greatest in-ring performers of his generation. During his decorated career, Styles has worked for the biggest promotions around the world and has a shared history with some of the biggest names in the wrestling industry. He is also known for his time in Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA, now known as Impact Wrestling) from 2002–2014 and New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) from 2014–2016.
